snippet.title: WAR 2 | Official Trailer | Hrithik Roshan | NTR | Kiara Advani | Ayan Mukerji | YRF Spy Universe
snippet.description:
Get ready for the storm, the WAR begins now! #War2Trailer is out!
#War2 releasing in Hindi, Telugu & Tamil on August 14th in cinemas worldwide! #YRFSpyUniverse

► Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/xs3mrY 🔔 Stay updated!
► YRF New Releases - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLCB05E03DA939D484

► Follow us on X: x.com/yrf

🎬 MOVIE CREDITS:
Movie: WAR 2
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, NTR, Kiara Advani
Director: Ayan Mukerji
Producer: Aditya Chopra
Co-Producer: Akshaye Widhani
Screenplay: Shridhar Raghavan
Director of Photography: Benjamin Jasper ACS 
Music: Pritam
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Dialogues: Abbas Tyrewala
Story: Aditya Chopra
Associate Producer: Rishabh Chopra
Executive Producer: Sanjay Shivalkar
Editor: Aarif Sheikh
Production Designers: Rajat Poddar, Amrita Mahal Nakai
Sound: Dileep Subramaniam, Ganesh Gangadharan
Background Music: Sanchit Balhara, Ankit Balhara
Action Directors: Spiro Razatos, Franz Spilhaus, Anl Arasu, Oh Sea Young, Craig Macrae, Sunil Rodrigues [ROD]
Costume Designers: Anaita Shroff Adajania, Niharika Jolly
Director of Choreography: Bosco Leslie Martis
Visual Effects Studio: yFX
Casting Director: Shanoo Sharma
Supervising Producer: Gurpreet Singh
Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney
Release Date: 14 August 2025

The film will be available with audio descriptions and closed captioning.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

#KINGDOM ~ Starring Vijay Deverakonda in Lead Role. Directed by Gowtam Tinnanuri. Music by Anirudh Ravichander. Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya Under Sithara Entertainments & Fortune 4 Cinemas Banner. Presented by Srikara Studios.

#Kingdom will roar in theatres Worldwide on July 31st! 👊🏾

Two Modes. Two Champions. One Legacy. 🌟 TEZ FFMIC is HERE!

This is the ultimate test of skill. We're setting the stage for 48 of India’s top teams to battle it out for supremacy in both Battle Royale and Clash Squad mode!

This is where legends are forged and players Reignite the Fire. Don't miss a second of the action.

📺 Don’t forget to tune in every week on the following dates:

🎯 Online Qualifiers
📅 July 26 – 27: Week 1 - 1:30 PM IST
📅 August 2: Week 2 - 1:30 PM IST
📅 August 3: Week 2 - 5:30 PM IST

#TEZ #FFMIC #FFM #Booyah

હે એ એ એ વાળ વાળ વાળ  મારી વેળા તુ વેળા વાળ
હે એ એ એ વાળ વાળ વાળ  મારી વેળા તુ વેળા વાળ
દેવી દશામાં તુ વેળા તુ વાળ 
તાર તાર તુ તાર મારી પેઢી તુ તાર
દેવી દશામાં વેળા તુ વાળ
હે એ એ એ આય આય આય મારી વાળે તુ આય 
વાગડ વાળી માતા વારે તુ આવ...
વાળ વાળ વાળ તુ વેળા તુ વાળ 
દેવી દશામાં તુ વેળા તુ વાળ...

માં તારા દીવા થી ઘર માં અજવાળુ 
અમને આલ્યુ તે રાજ ને રજવાડુ 
હો દશામાં દશામાં રાટ કરું તારુ 
ડગલે ને પગલે તને ના વિહારુ 
હે એ એ એ ભાળ ભાળ ભાળ મારી હામે તુ ભાળ 
દેવી દશામાં તુ વેળા તુ વાળ
વાળ વાળ વાળ તુ વેળા તુ વેળા તુ વાળ
દેવી દશામાં વેળા તુ વાળ... 

હો તારા હામે નજર ધરી પાટ તારો ઢાળુ 
મારે તો તુ ખમ્મા કે એજ અજવાળુ 
હા માતા ની દયા થી અમે અલગ ને અનોખા
કિસ્મત સિતારા ના પાડવા દીધા નોખા
હે એ એ એ વાળ વાય  વાય  વાય સુખ ના વાયરા વાય 
તુ મળી એને લીલા લેર થાય
વાળ વાળ વાળ તુ મારી વેળા તુ વાળ 
દેવી દશામાં વેળા તુ વાળ
હે દેવી દશામાં વેળા તુ વાળ...
---------------------

snippet.title: Paraya Baap | Official Trailer | Yash Kumarr & Nidhi Mishra | Bhojpuri Movie 2025
snippet.description:
जन्म देने वाले से बड़ा जीवन देने वाला होता है। फिल्म "पराया बाप" का फर्स्ट लुक ट्रेलर

भोजपुरी सुपरस्टार यश कुमार की नई फिल्म "पराया बाप" का धमाकेदार ऑफिशियल ट्रेलर 2025 अब आ चुका है। यह फिल्म रिश्तों, बलिदान और इंसानियत की सच्चाई को दिखाने वाली एक भावनात्मक कहानी है। इस फिल्म के डायरेक्टर रुस्तम अली चिश्ती है। इस फिल्म में मुख्य भूमिका में यश कुमार और अन्य कई कलाकार है।

◾ निर्माता - यश कुमार इन्टरटेनमेन्ट व निधि मिश्रा
◾ निर्देशक - रूस्तम अली चिश्ती
◾ संगीत - साजन मिश्रा
◾ गीत - राजेश मिश्रा, धरम हिन्दुस्तानी
◾ कथा - यश कुमार
◾ पटकथा - यश कुमार व एस. के. चौहान
◾ संवाद - मनोज गुप्ता
◾ छायांकन - जहाँगीर सय्यद
◾ संकलन - रंजीत प्रसाद
◾ नृत्य - प्रवीण शेलार
◾ कार्यकारी निर्माता - शैलेन्द्र सिंह
◾ कला - रविन्द्रनाथ गुप्ता
◾ प्रोमो एडिटर - एम. फैसल रियाज़
◾ कास्टयूम - विद्या-विष्णु
◾ पोस्ट प्रोडक्शन - टी. आर. पी. स्टूडियोज
◾ पार्श्व संगीत - राजा यादव
◾ डी आई - स्वआनंद करणेकर
◾ सह निर्देशक - स्वाती यादव
◾ स्टिल - पंकज सक्सेना
◾ डिजाइन - नसु

📝 कहानी:
फिल्म पराया बाप एक संवेदनशील और भावनात्मक कहानी को पर्दे पर उतारती है। यह कहानी रिश्तों, बलिदान, और इंसानियत के उस सच को उजागर करती है जहां जन्म देने वाले से बड़ा जीवन देने वाला माना जाता है। फिल्म में यश कुमार की दमदार अदाकारी और निधि मिश्रा की शानदार परफॉर्मेंस दर्शकों को बांधकर रखेगी।

📌 फिल्म के मुख्य आकर्षण:
▪ यश कुमार का पावरफुल किरदार और डायलॉग्स
▪ दिल छू लेने वाला संगीत और कर्णप्रिय गाने
▪ एक मजबूत सामाजिक संदेश देने वाली कहानी
▪ भोजपुरी इंडस्ट्री के टॉप स्टार्स की बेहतरीन एक्टिंग

snippet.title: War 2 Trailer REVIEW | Suraj Kumar
snippet.description:
The trailer for War 2 is finally here — and it’s a high-octane, star-packed ride featuring Hrithik Roshan, NTR Jr, and Kiara Advani. But does it live up to the massive expectations set by the first film? We break down every frame of this adrenaline-fueled trailer, from the stylish action sequences to the YRF Spy Universe connections.

Is War 2 just another spectacle or does it hint at a story with depth? Are Hrithik and NTR Jr. set to be the greatest rivals of the franchise? And how does this film tie in with Pathaan, Tiger, and the rest of the spy saga?

Let’s find out in this trailer breakdown and review.

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: War 2 Trailer Review ⋮ Looks Big… Feels Flat
snippet.description:
War 2’s trailer is definitely an upgrade from the teaser, offering some narrative intrigue and character stakes — especially with Kabir going rogue and Jr. NTR hunting him down. But the generic action, weak VFX, and over-the-top spectacle kill the excitement, leaving behind a flashy yet emotionally flat experience. #War2 #PJExplained #thePJ

hi.title: War 2 Trailer Review ⋮ Looks Big… Feels Flat
hi.description:
War 2’s trailer is definitely an upgrade from the teaser, offering some narrative intrigue and character stakes — especially with Kabir going rogue and Jr. NTR hunting him down. But the generic action, weak VFX, and over-the-top spectacle kill the excitement, leaving behind a flashy yet emotionally flat experience. #War2 #PJExplained #thePJ

snippet.title: Jigar Thakor | Ghare Padharya Dashama | ઘરે પધાર્યા દશામાં | New Dashama Song 2025 | Jhankar Music
snippet.description:
Jhankar Music Bhakti Gujarati Presents Latest Dashama Devotional Video Song titled "Ghare Padharya Dashama", Sung by Jigar Thakor, & Penned by Viral Nayta, & Music Directed by Dhaval Patel, Prabhat Thakor Undra, Starring: Jigar Thakor, Bharti Thakor, Raj Chaudhary, & Directed by Naresh Patani, Prakash Vadhasar
Stay tuned & Subscribe Our Yt Channel to get Notified-
https://www.youtube.com/c/JhankarMusicGujaratiBhakti  

Here's to make your busy morning beautiful, introducing "Dashama Padharya", a peaceful devotional song to mend your hearts.

તમારી વ્યસ્ત સવારને સુંદર બનાવવા માટે, "દશામાં પધાર્યા" રજૂ કરી રહ્યા છીએ, જે તમારા હૃદયને શાંત કરવા માટે એક શાંતિપૂર્ણ ભક્તિ ગીત છે.

To Make Insta Reels Click here : https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1454037235634476/

🎧 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Song : Ghare Padharya Dashama 
♪ Singer : Jigar  Thakor
♪ Lyrics : Viral Nayta, Vikram Abluva
♪ Music : Dhaval Patel, Prabhat Thakor Undra
♪ Studio : Jhankar Music Recording Studio - Patan

🎬 𝐕𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Producer : Maarss Movies And Music (Jhankar Music)
♪ Project Lead By : Vikram Abluva
♪ Director : Naresh Patani, Prakash Vadhasar
♪ Star Cast : Jigar Thakor, Bharti Thakor, Raj Chaudhary
♪ Co Artist : Dharti Parmar, Mital Parmar
♪ D.O.P, Editing & DI : Naresh Patani
♪ Production :  VAT Digital - Patan
♪ Makeup : Bharti Thakor
♪ Design : P.C. Patan 
♪ SP Thanks : Alkesh Abluva, Mehul Abluva
♪ Travelling : Jayesh Thakor
♪ Genre : Devotional
♪ Music Label : Jhankar Music
📞For enquiries and for Song Uploading Contact on this No.: 7383909868

#jigarthakor #newdashamasong #dashamanagarba #gharepadharyadashama #jhankarmusicbhaktigujarati 
---------------------------------
📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: Gujarati  👇

હો અષાઢ ઉતરીયો શ્રાવણ આયો ઝરમર મેઘ વરસ્યા...(૨)
ઘેર દશામાં પધાર્યા 
હે આયો દિવાહા નો દાડો 
મારા હૈયે હરખ લાયો દશામાં વધાવો
હો દશ દાડા દશામાં ના વ્રત મારે લેવા
હાજ હવાર માંની કરવી મારે સેવા
હે આજે આભે વીજ ચમકી મધુરા મોર બોલ્યા
મારા ઘેર દશામાં પધાર્યા...(૨)

હો શક્તિ પ્રમાણે માડી કરુ તારી ભક્તિ
આવવા ના દેતી કોઈ દાડો મારી નમતી
હો આજે મારી હાલત જોઇ હશે ભલે વસતી 
દશામાં બનાવશે મને બહુ મોટી હસ્તી
હો દીવો તારો ભરું માં અજવાળા કાયમ રાખજે...(૨)
અમી નજરું મારા માથે માડી નાખજે
હો દયાળુ દશામાં તું દુઃખિયા ની બેલી
કાયમ રેજે ભેળી ...(૨)

હો પૂરા કરજે જે મેં જોયા સે સપના 
જોજે કોડ અધુરા ન રહી જાય મારા મનના
હો મારા માટે માડી તું રામ લેખ ધડજે
દૂબળા દાડા માડી તું ના આવવા દેજે 
હો કાળા કળયુગ તારા મોજુદાશે પારચા
દેવી દશામાં ની તો જગ માં થાય ચરચા 
હો સુખ નો સુરજ મળી તું મારા ઘેર ઉગાડજે 
મારી વેળા માં તું વાળજે...(૩)

Watch our other songs click here: 👇
 
► માં - Maa (Jigar Ni Jeet)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CProTe4A3cc

►Dashma No Bajot
https://youtu.be/PtwQcgbSuOM

 ►Dashama Ni Aarti
https://youtu.be/uFLRp_aw-Mg

►Manthi Monu Tane Dashama 
https://youtu.be/GiXg_PRsCIM

►Mari Das Dishani Dasha Maa
https://youtu.be/P7OpOGlWzI8

snippet.description:

-----------------
Song: Naane Neenanthe
Lyrics- Shashank
Pallavi: 
ನಾನೇ- ನೀನಂತೆ ನೀನಂತೆ 
ನೀನೇ- ನಾನಂತೆ ನಾನಂತೆ 
ಜೀವಾ..ಒಂದೇನೆ,ಹೃದಯ ಎರಡು 

ನಮ್ಮ- ನಡುವೆ ಬರಲಿ ನೂರು- ಮುನಿಸು ಜಗಳ 
ಹಾಗೆ.. ಇರಲಿ ಪ್ರೀತಿ ಸೊಗಡು

ಜೊತೆಯಲಿ ನೀನಿದ್ದರೆ ಎದೆಯಲಿ ಸಡಗರ 
ನಿನ್ನ ನಗು ಎಲ್ಲದಕ್ಕೂ ಪರಿಹಾರ

ನನ್ನಯ ನಾಳೆ- ನಿನ್ನಯ ಪಾಲೆ ನನ್ನಾ ಬದುಕೆ ನಿನ್ನದು ಗೆಳತಿ.

ಕಾಯುವೆ ನಾನು- ರೆಪ್ಪೆಯ ಹಾಗೆ  ಜನುಮ ಪೂರಾ ನಿನ್ನನ್ನೇ..
ಕೋರುವೆ ನಿನ್ನ- ಗಾಳಿಯ ಹಾಗೆ  ಉಸಿರು ಇರೋ ತನಕಾನೆ..
ಚರಣ: 1:
ಬದುಕಿನ ಕೊರತೆಯನು ತುಂಬಿಂದ ನಾಯಕಿಯೇ

snippet.title: WAR 2 Trailer Reaction! | Hrithik Roshan | NTR | Kiara Advani | YRF Spy Universe
snippet.description:
Jaby & Achara react to the pulse-pounding trailer for War 2—a high-octane, cinematic showdown that’s set to take the YRF Spy Universe to explosive new heights.

Returning as the enigmatic super-soldier Kabir, Hrithik Roshan (Fighter, War) faces off against a powerful new force—N. T. Rama Rao Jr. (RRR, Janatha Garage)—in a battle where loyalties blur and the cost of war runs deeper than ever. Directed by Ayan Mukerji (Brahmāstra, Wake Up Sid), this sequel raises the bar with breathtaking scale, emotionally charged conflict, and edge-of-your-seat action.

From globe-trotting espionage and gritty hand-to-hand combat to larger-than-life stunts and an electrifying score, the War 2 trailer delivers pure cinematic adrenaline. Vivian & Brandon break it all down—the mind games, the mythic rivalries, and the epic visuals that hint at something far bigger than just a battle between two men.

This isn't just a fight. It's a reckoning. And if the trailer is anything to go by, War 2 is set to become a genre-defining spectacle.

____________________

snippet.description:
About SHINE HUNT :
* On our channel we create а trailer teaser *
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer teaser Glimpse are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film..
The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely .                                      .----SHINE HUNT CHANNEL----

snippet.title: WE OUTSIDE | YELHOMIE | OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO | @massappealindia
snippet.description:
We Outside by Yelhomie with Augustine Shimray and Sajou Chenglei.

Stream We Outside: https://orcd.co/weoutside_yelhomie

Label: Mass Appeal

Song description:
“We Outside” is not just a track it’s a defiant anthem born from pain, protest, and resistance. Written amidst curfews, gunshots, and internet blackouts in war-torn Manipur, Yelhomie confronts state violence, systemic oppression, and the harsh realities faced by his Indigenous community during the 2023 conflict.
Opening with a haunting tribal chant “Carry the shield, hold the spear” sung by Augustine from Featherheads (Ukhrul, Manipur), the song sets the tone for a battle cry steeped in ancestral strength. Produced by Seej from Mizoram, the beat fuses Indigenous tribal textures with raw hip-hop grit, giving voice to a region often left in 
silence.

With hard-hitting bars like “Heavier the pants, the dreams don’t fly”, Yelhomie captures the tragic transformation of students and dreamers into reluctant warriors. The youth, once full of ambition, now carry arms not by choice, but by necessity, victims of a system that fuels chaos to suppress dissent.

The outro features a spiritual invocation in Ancient Meitei-lon written in Meitei Mayek script — a wake-up call to the Yel-hou-mee, the Indigenous people of Manipur, delivered by Oja Sajoubi Chenglei of the Puya temple board (Puya refers to the holy book of Sanamahism, religion of the indigenous Meitei people). Under the shadow of a banyan tree, the elder chants:
“Do we have to live like grass under their foot? 
Wake up, Yelhoumee, sons and daughters of the Salai Taret!”
Here, Salai Taret refers to the seven clan lineages (Salai) and "Taret" means seven in Meitei-lon.
This powerful moment bridges the past and present—a cry for unity and cultural survival.
“We Outside” is a song for those who have been silenced — a voice for the displaced, the grieving, and the unbroken. It belongs on playlists that spotlight politically charged rap, regional resistance, raw lyricism, and the emerging fire of East Indian hip-hop.

A film by Hype 79
Director - Krishna Thokchom
Cinematography/Editor - Narry Takhellambam
Drone - Abung
VFX - Naocha

Cast - Augustine Shimray (Featherheads), Oja Sajoubi (Outro), Joy Khundrakpam, Rajkumari Nevia, Mangal Kshetrimayum

Child Artist - Sinthalemba Nongthombam Meitei

Audio Credits:
Produced by Seej
Mixed and mastered by Skar

Video credits
Crew - Malem Sanasam, Rajesh Khaidem, Abung Wairokpam, Ronaldson Takhellambam, Adanial Tokpam, David, Sanathoi Ngairangbam, Niketan Akoijam, Hijam Sanatomba, Totto Thokchom, Skar, Nganba Sanoujam, Chinglen Nongthomgbam, Martin kaidem, Bishal Laisram, Thoithoiba Thokchom, Alish Nongthongbam, Trilokchand Posungbam, Malemnganba Mangsatabam, Somorjit khangebam, Devjit Yumnam, Mahesh Phijam, Lakhan Ngangom, Robinson Wakabam, Amaraj Leiphoubam, Rajesh Pebam, Sunildro Nongthombam, Parihanba Posungbam, AT Heingang Unit 33, Kanglei Hoops, Jonarth Seram, Jupiter Ningombam, Bilson Ngairangbam, Dingku Heisnam, Benish Leishangthem, Newton Thoidingjam, Ronan Warepam, Nelson Sharma, Ngouren Ningombam, Langamba Leiphrakpam, Leishemba Leishangthem, Prince Achom, Tyson Ngangbam, Prithiviraj Sarangthem, Meerel, Richard Rajkumar, Allen (chaoba), Tangku, Darick, Lamboikhongnangkhong gi ema ebel meira paibi sing

snippet.title: AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH - Trailer (2025) James Cameron | 20th century studios
snippet.description:
#avatar #jamescameron #disney 

— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

—  In this concept trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash, Pandora reveals a darker side as old loyalties fracture and new fires take hold. Varang, leader of the Ash People, turns away from Eywa and leads a rising Na’vi clan that bends flame to its will, threatening not only balance but belief itself. Jake Sully, still bearing the weight of Neteyam’s loss, must hold his family together as they face not just the returning human forces, but a war born from within their own kind. Spider stands at a crossroads between the man who raised him and the father who now wears a Na’vi face, while Kiri, Lo’ak, and Tuk each grapple with grief and transformation. With striking images of scorched cliffs, skyborne fleets, and firelit battlegrounds, the trailer paints a portrait of a story defined by legacy, fracture, and the unshaken bond of family: whatever comes, Sullys face it as one.
 
—  Subscribe to Teaser Universe 🎬

snippet.title: Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan 2 - Trailer | Karamjit Anmol | In Cinemas 08 Aug | New Punjabi Movie
snippet.description:
🎬Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan 2 – Official Trailer Releasing in Cinemas this Rakhi – August 8th, 2025

Presented by Ranjiv Singla Productions, this heartfelt sequel to the beloved Punjabi hit "Kuriyan Jawan Bapu Preshaan" brings back the powerful story of a father and his four daughters — filled with laughter, love, and life’s beautiful struggles.

👨‍👧‍👧 Celebrate this Rakhi with a story that honors the unbreakable bond between a father and his daughters. Only in theatres from August 8th, 2025.

🎞 Credits
📽 Produced by: Ranjiv Singla
✍ Story & Directed by: Avtar Singh
🖊 Written by: Aman Sidhu
🌟 Starring: Karamjit Anmol, Sukhwinder Raj, Ekta Gulati Khera, Gunveen Manchanda, Avnoor, Mannat Sharma, Pooja Gaba, Raj Dhaliwal, Arry Gill
🎥 Cinematography: Navneet Beohar
✂ Editor: Krishna Rodge
🎵 Music: Amdad Ali, RD Beat
🎤 Singers: Karamjit Anmol, Nachhatar Gill, Rza Heer, Anmol Virk
🎶 Lyrics: Gurbinder Maan, Jaggi Jagsir, Gurri Billing
🎚 Re-Recording Mixing: After Play Studios (Maddy)
🎛 Mixer: Anish Poduval
🎨 Art Director: Balkar Singh (Rustom)
👗 Costume Designer: Asmita Chauhan
🎞 Post Production: Master Prime Studios
📋 Line Production: Vikramjit
📲 Digital Promotion: Creative Benchers
https://www.creativebenchers.com/
🎥 Creative Producer: Inder Bansal
🎬 Executive Producer: Rajinder Kumar Gagahar
🖼 Publicity Design: Aman Kalsi
💻 VFX & Graphics: 2DS Film Studio
📽 Visual Promotion: Visual Key Studios
🎞 Motion Graphics: Junaid Ansari
💄 Makeup & Hair: Alpesh, Abhishek & Kia
🎼 Original Background Score: Siddharth Malla , Punnet Porpanth 
🌍 Worldwide Distribution: The Next Film Studio
🎶 Music On: RR Records

❤ A film for every daughter. A salute to every father.

Free All Rewards Naruto Chapter 2 😲 | free fire Naruto Chapter 2 Event |

Welcome to my Deep Dive into NARUTO CHAPTER 2 – Latest Free Fire MAX × Naruto Ninja War Collab!

In this video, I’ve covered EVERYTHING you need to know:

How to claim free rewards – Mystery Shop pass, daily headbands, and completing "Epic Ninja Trials".

How & when to unlock the Itachi Super Bundle, Naruto bundles, Madara bundle, Orochimaru & Minato bundles, and get the Susano Emote for free (if you draw 4 bundles!)  

Step‑by‑step in‑game interface walkthrough – where to click, avoid pitfalls, and ensure no mistake in the claiming process.

Review of new Super Emote animations like Flying Raijin Jutsu, Reanimation Jutsu, Final Battle Emote, Forehead Poke Emote, Fireball Jutsu & more  

Character changes & abilities tested – Itachi’s Amaterasu stealth illusions, Hinata’s Byakugan support play, Gaara sand‑control area buffs, Madara’s Susanoo ultimate power abilities  


⏳ Launch & Timing

Expected live from July 31, 2025, with OB50 update across servers; Chapter 2 rolls out first week of August 2025  


✅ Avoid these key mistakes:

1. Missing daily headband missions—skip them and delay rewards.


2. Enter the wrong menu – follow my Nitro “Mystery Shop → Ninja Trials” path to get free bundles.


3. Stop before drawing 4 bundles—must do 4 to get the free Susano Emote

⭐Song : Aayi Aayi Teej Dekho Aayi
⭐Singer : Upasana Mehta & Maya Goswami & Others
⭐Lyrics : Tarditional & Others
⭐Music: Binny Narang 
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma
⭐Content Manager : Dev Taneja 
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)

⭐⭐⭐अपने दिन को बेहतर बनाने व् अपने कृष्णा जी के नए नए सुन्दर सुन्दर भजन रोज सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़े रहे || स्वस्थ रहें मस्त रहें || जय श्री कृष्णा ||⭐⭐⭐

⭐⭐⭐ हम आप लोगो को अच्छे - अच्छे सुन्दर भजन आल्हा गाथा , कँवर भजन , शिव भजन , माता भजन , छठ गीत , श्याम भजन , और राधा कृष्ण भजन लेकर आपको ऐसी ही सुनते रहेंगे 
आशा है की आप हमारे इस चैनल को ऐसे ही प्यार दुलार और आशीर्वाद देते रहेंगे

तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए। सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण होंगी । 🙏

 रोज नए नए भजन सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़ें रहे व् नए नए भजनों का आनंद उठाये भजन पसंद आये तो कमेंट में '' जय श्री श्याम " जरुर लिखें || 🌹🌹

⭐Song : आया तीज का त्योहार 
खुशियों की तीज मनाऊँगी 
मैं सावन तीज मनाऊँगी 
सावन में झूले राधा संग बनवारी 
आई आई तीज देखो आई
झूला झूलादो म्हाने कृष्ण कन्हैया
कौन कहता है भगवान 
ऐसा झूला दिया राधा को श्याम 
सावन की पड़े बौछार राधा भीग रही
सांवली सूरत पे मोहन दिल दीवाना

⭐Lyrics : Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)

snippet.title: Maa | মা | Dhumketu | Anupam Roy | Dev | Kaushik Ganguly | New Bengali Movie Song | বাংলা গান
snippet.description:
"মা" একটি হৃদয়স্পর্শী নতুন বাংলা গান যা প্রতিভাবান অনুপম রায়ের লেখা, সুর করা এবং গাওয়া। আসন্ন ছবি "ধুমকেতু" থেকে এই মর্মস্পর্শী গানটি মা এবং সন্তানের মধ্যে চিরন্তন বন্ধনকে ব্যক্ত করে,

Experience the deep emotional resonance of "Maa", a heart-touching new Bengali song composed, written, and sung by the incredibly talented Anupam Roy. This poignant track from the upcoming film Dhumketu captures the timeless bond between a mother and child, blending heartfelt lyrics with soul-stirring melodies.

আপনার পছন্দের ভালো গান শুনতে সাবস্ক্রাইব করুন  @saregamabengali

snippet.title: Javu Gamatre - Gopal Bharwad  - Sunita Bharwad - 4K Video - Latest Gujarati Song 2025
snippet.description:
Song: Javu Gamatre
Singer: Gopal Bharwad, Sunita Bharwad
Artists: Samarth Sharma, Chhaya Thakor
Co - Artists: Sunil Kachhiya, Jagruti Goswami, Vicky Rajput
Music: Sunil Thakor, Jaydeep Patel
Lyrics: Hari Bharwad
Co-Ordinator: Indar Gamara
D.O.P.: Chanakya Thakor
Edit: Montu Rajput
BGM: Rajendrasinh
Director: Vishnu Thakor - Adalaj
Producer: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics Of This Song:

Mara Piyu Ae Mari Hatu Bandhya Bangala Mangamata
Mara Vhal Na Virada Ma Aanhu Kharu No Dholata
Bethi Orada Na Hu To Ekali Haiya Re Radata
Aava Het Na Hathila Ven Kadava No Bolata
Tara Vina Re Aankhe Na Mataku
Jova Re Hu To Pal Pal Tadapu
Tu Halyo Gamatre
Tame Karo Na Aam Bhina Odhana
Lai Leshu Ame Tam Thi Abolada
Javu Re Padashe
Tara Lakh Na Re Bangala Joi Haiya Re Radata
Tame Haiye Rakhi Het Vhali Mathu No Bolata

Ho Virah Ghereli Vedanayu Tamne Nai Hamajay
Avalu Odhyu Odhanu Tamthi Joyu Kem Jay
Ho Hamjo Hathili Ham Mara Pida Na Sahevay
Karam Futyu Maru Vhali Bhav Adhura Thay
Te Choriye Fariya Fera Char
Redha Meli Na Mane Ranzal
Tu Halyo Gamatare
Ho Jiv Melata Jiv Maro Lajjay
Vidhi Na Lekh Avala No Lakhay
Javu Gamatare
Mara Piyu Ae Melya Amne Aaj Redha Re Ran Ma
Aava Het Na Hathili Vhali Mara Kalajada Kor Ma

Ho Pujyo Paras Pepado Ne Kariya Ghana Vrat Re
Meli Jiv Ne Redho Tu To Haliyo Gamatare
Ho Hamjo Ne Vhali Vat Mari Nathi Het Ma Khot
Papan Na Palalo Vhali Hasta Rakho Hoth
Aa Sakhiyo Hare Manakho Maro
Abhagiyo Aa Bhav Maro
Tu Halyo Gamatre
Ho Aanhude Na Tame Antar Balo
Hasata Modhe Amne Valavo
Javu Gamatre
Mara Piyu Ae Mari Hatu Bandhya Bangla Mangamata
Ho Het Na Hathili Vhali Ven Kadava No Bolata
